# Content Reporting & Moderation

The AETHEL administration team is committed to maintaining a professional and safe environment. 

### Reporting Process
To report inappropriate content (comments, code snippets, or documentation) that violates our Code of Conduct:
1. Send an email to `conduct@aethel-project.org`.
2. Provide a link to the content and a brief explanation of the violation.

### Resolution Tiers
| Tier | Action | Criteria |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **I** | Warning | Minor violation, first-time offense. |
| **II** | Removal | Toxic content or repeated minor violations. |
| **III** | Permanent Ban | Severe harassment, hate speech, or malicious intent. |

Reports are reviewed within **72 hours**. Confidentiality of the reporter is strictly maintained.
